functions.name: CanCompileWithBaseline
functions.logic: Determines whether a given SharedFunctionInfo can be compiled using the Baseline compiler.

functions.name: GenerateBaselineCode
functions.logic: Generates baseline code for the given SharedFunctionInfo.

functions.name: EmitReturnBaseline
functions.logic: Emits the necessary instructions for a return statement within the Baseline compiler using the provided MacroAssembler.
